This document has reproduction restrictions under InfoSoc Directive 2001/29/EC.
- Extract ONLY factual information (prices, fees, transaction volumes, thresholds).
- Do NOT reproduce verbatim text from this document.
- Paraphrase all excerpts. Do not quote directly.
- The source_excerpt field must contain a paraphrase, not a direct quote.
"""
```

### For BLOCKED Documents â Never Sent to LLM

```python
