## ð TDM Compliance Checklist

### Pre-Processing

- [ ] **Lawful access verification**: Does the system have lawful access to the document?
- [ ] **Opt-out scan**: Run AI opt-out pattern check on first 3,000 chars
- [ ] **Reproduction rights scan**: Check for "All Rights Reserved" patterns
- [ ] **Source URL check**: For online sources, check robots.txt and HTML meta tags
- [ ] **License declaration review**: Has the uploader declared the document license?

### During Processing

- [ ] **BLOCKED documents**: Return HTTP 451, log, notify Admin â never pass to LLM
- [ ] **RESTRICTED documents**: Add paraphrase instruction to system prompt
- [ ] **All documents**: Include source citation instruction in system prompt
- [ ] **Output validation**: Verify no verbatim text from RESTRICTED docs in output

### Post-Processing

- [ ] **Status recording**: Update `documents.copyright_status` in the database
- [ ] **Audit log**: Record opt-out detection results in `guardrail_audit`
- [ ] **Blocked doc escalation**: Admin notified for all BLOCKED documents
- [ ] **Paraphrase verification**: Review RESTRICTED doc source_excerpts are paraphrased

