## ðĻ Enforcement Consequences

**Processing a document after detecting a valid Art. 4 opt-out constitutes:**

- Copyright infringement under InfoSoc Directive 2001/29/EC (Art. 2)
- Potential EU AI Act violation (Art. 53(1)(c) for GPAI providers)
- Exposure to injunctions, damages, and statutory penalties under IPRED Directive 2004/48/EC
- In France: potential AFNOR/INPI enforcement action
- In Germany: potential injunction under Â§Â§ 44a, 44b UrhG (German copyright transposition)
